com.blukii.sdk.config

Interface DataManager.OnSyncListener

  • Enclosing class:
    DataManager

    public static interface DataManager.OnSyncListener

    The listener interface for receiving state changes from syncing blukiis with blukii cloud. Implementations of this interface get notified when a synchronization is done or an error occurred while synchronizing blukiis with blukii cloud.
